comments: As Porzingis (WAS) is moving on the perimeter, incidental lower-body contact occurs with Martin (MIA).
Goodwin (WAS) and Lowry (MIA) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
After Herro (MIA) secures the rebound, Kuzma (WAS) is still moving toward the ball, causing marginal contact to occur.
Goodwin (WAS) wraps Adebayo (MIA) as he releases to roll to the basket and the contact affects his FOM.
As Adebayo (MIA) is firming up for the pick, he places his hands and brushes them against Kuzma (WAS), and the contact is marginal.
Herro (MIA) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Herro (MIA) is moving alongside Kuzma's (WAS) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together at the start of the drive.
Adebayo (MIA) brings his hand toward Beal (WAS) and marginal contact occurs as he releases away to roll.
Porzingis (WAS) jumps alongside Adebayo (MIA) and marginal body contact occurs during his shot attempt near the rim.
Porzingis (WAS) commits a take foul on Martin (MIA). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Martin (MIA) has his foot planted on the ground when incidental contact occurs between the ball and his leg/foot.
Martin (MIA) legally contests Beal's (WAS) jump shot attempt.
